description:
Kimberly Reed is transgender and forced to confront her past and future when she attends her father&rsquo;s funeral.&nbsp;&nbsp;
Ishmael Beah is the author of A Long Way Gone: Memoirs of a Boy Soldier.&nbsp;
Laura Revness and her family&rsquo;s parrot, Pumpkin, must redefine the pecking order.&nbsp;
Bobby Stoddard is young and in love, but struggles with his girlfriend&rsquo;s one-year prison sentence.When offensive or FCC-prohibited words appear, they are bleeped and listed in the Content Advisory. Sensitive content will be given an on-air caution and will be noted here in the description.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
